---
title: Sticky Apricot Chicken with Garlic Crushed Potatoes & Steamed Veggies
description: For tonight’s dinner, we’ve enlisted the help of a lively glaze made with BBQ sauce: it coats each bite of tender
chicken thigh in sticky smokiness and even tastes great drizzled over the robust steamed veggies and crushed
potatoes. Go for your life!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
